target: dependency1 dependency2 ...
[tab]action

//see included Makefile

//execute by command :

$ make

//running make in given directory the MAkefile is red and the listed operations are executed
// at the end we shoud get our "program.bin" just like if we complied our program manually

// of course all the upper stands for the casese make and gcc tools are both installed properly
